              </h3>

              <!-- Chiffres clés -->
              <div class="flex gap-3 mb-6">
                <div class="flex-1 p-4 bg-white/15 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">3+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-orange-100">années</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 p-4 bg-white/15 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">IA</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-orange-100">× Craft</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Outils -->
              <div class="mb-6">
                <p class="text-xs text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Outils maîtrisés</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">Claude Code</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">MCP</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">Skills</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">Hooks</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">Commands</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">Plugins</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">RAG</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">n8n</span>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/15 rounded text-sm text-white">GitHub Copilot</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Colonne droite : contenu -->
          <div class="md:col-span-8 md:pl-8 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                L'IA change notre façon de coder.
                Mais sans direction, elle amplifie les problèmes autant que les solutions.
              </p>

              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                Je t'aide à intégrer les outils d'automatisation dans tes workflows — pour gagner en productivité sans sacrifier la qualité.
              </p>

              <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 mt-0.5 text-xl">✓</span>
                  <span>Intégration Claude Code / agents IA</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 mt-0.5 text-xl">✓</span>
                  <span>Workflows automatisés</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 mt-0.5 text-xl">✓</span>
                  <span>Garde-fous qualité</span>
                </li>
              </ul>

              <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-orange-300 pl-4 py-3 mb-6 bg-orange-50 rounded-r-lg">
                <p class="text-gray-700 italic">« Ce que j'aime dans l'automatisation : trouver le bon équilibre entre vitesse et garde-fous. Aller vite, mais pas droit dans le mur. »</p>
              </blockquote>

              <a
                href="/automatisation"
                class="inline-block bg-orange-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-orange-800 transition-colors text-lg"
              >
                En savoir plus →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

